</p>
<p>III.  UNDERLYING HUMAN RIGHTS VIOLATIONS &#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230; &#8230; 10 
</p>
<p>A.  Corruption and violations of economic and social rights 
</p>
<p>B.  Lack of accountability for human rights violations and weak rule of  
</p>
<p> law institutions 
</p>
