</p>
<p>IV.  HUMAN RIGHTS VIOLATIONS RELATED TO THE  
</p>
<p>MAIDAN PROTESTS  &#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230; 13 
</p>
