</b></p>
<p> 
</p>
<p><b>Office of the United Nations High Commissioner  
</b></p>
<p><b>for Human Rights 
</b></p>
<p><b>  
</b></p>
<p><b> 
</b></p>
<p><b> 
</b></p>
<p><b> 
</b></p>
<p><b>Report on the human rights situation in Ukraine 
</b></p>
<p><b>15 May 2014 
</b></p>
<p><b> 
</b></p>
<p> </p>

<p><b>30 | </b>P a g e <b> 
</b></p>
<p> 
</p>
